VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \(\s*\w+\s*\*\)\s*malloc\s*
WHEN EXPR MISSING:// intentional|// cast required|static_cast|reinterpret_cast && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects unnecessary casting of `malloc()` results.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Incorrect Casting of malloc() Results.
